nodes.text: Dal Zorfenn was a male Nagai commander in the Nagai expeditionary force. Alongside his female subordinate, Lieutenant Cyn Jodu, Zorfenn was tasked with securing the planet Kinooine that it might serve as the primary base of operations for the Nagai fleet's planned invasion of the galaxy.
Zorfenn's name came from scrambling the letters of the name of Ron (Ronald) Frenz, the artist who drew the very first Nagai.
